data.description: Outstanding custom detached townhome near golf community. Beautiful architectural finishes & craftsmanship throughout. Gourmet kitchen has granite counters, SS appliances and wall ovens, large center island, hardwood floor & eat-in dining. Dining area includes desk & media storage. Spacious living room w/ elevated ceilings, custom built-ins, fireplace & tall windows. Enjoy the seasons on the updated deck with new floorboards & railings (23). Lovely owner’s ensuite has tiled floors, soaking tub, separate shower, linen closet & dual sinks. Did I mention two walk-in closets! Laundry room w/cabinet storage plus mudroom walk-in closet. Lower-level includes huge family room, gas fireplace & mini wet bar convenient for lounging & entertaining. Add’l baseboard heat keeps it cozy! Two large bedrooms w/big closets + a full bath! Huge storage room. Updates: roof, furnace w/humidifier, appliances, carpet, fans/light fixtures, paint, leaf guard gutters+. Garage chair lift is optional. Welcome home!
